11 however, the provisions of this clause (6), except for the first sentence, shall not apply to
12 contractors furnishing a performance and payment bond, lien or completion bond, or a bond
13 equivalent approved by the director of consumer affairs and business regulation covering a
14 minimum of two million dollars;
15 SECTION 2. Said section 2 of chapter 142A, as so appearing, is hereby further amended
16 by adding at the end thereof the following:-
17 Any violation of this section shall constitute an unfair method of competition or unfair or
